  "detailed_description": "<strong>ARTDINK \"Legend Pack\" Series</strong><br><br>The ARTDINK \"Legend Pack\" Series is a compilation of ARTDINK's masterpiece works of the 1980s and 1990s. The PC9800 versions of these games can finally be played in Windows. In addition, a Library Mode exclusive to the \"Legend Pack\" allows you to browse illustrations, graphic and sound data.<br><br>\"Eikan wa Kimi ni Legend Pack\" is a compilation containing the following titles:<br>\"Eikan wa Kimi ni\" (original release 1990/07)<br>\"Eikan wa Kimi ni 2\" (original release 1991/06)<br>\"Eikan wa Kimi ni 3\" (original release 1993/07)<br><br>The \"Eikan wa Kimi ni\" series is a high school baseball simulation where you become a coach and guide your team to Koshien.<br><br><strong>This game is only available in Japanese.</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>ARTDINK \"Legend Pack\" Series</strong><br><br>The ARTDINK \"Legend Pack\" Series is a compilation of ARTDINK's masterpiece works of the 1980s and 1990s. The PC9800 versions of these games can finally be played in Windows. In addition, a Library Mode exclusive to the \"Legend Pack\" allows you to browse illustrations, graphic and sound data.<br><br>\"Eikan wa Kimi ni Legend Pack\" is a compilation containing the following titles:<br>\"Eikan wa Kimi ni\" (original release 1990/07)<br>\"Eikan wa Kimi ni 2\" (original release 1991/06)<br>\"Eikan wa Kimi ni 3\" (original release 1993/07)<br><br>The \"Eikan wa Kimi ni\" series is a high school baseball simulation where you become a coach and guide your team to Koshien.<br><br><strong>This game is only available in Japanese.</strong>",
